definitions.definition: A person who is recognized by a university as having completed the requirements of a degree studied at the institution.
A person who is recognized by a high school as having completed the requirements of a course of study at the school.
A person who is recognized as having completed any level of education.
A graduated (marked) cup or other container , thus fit for measuring.
